---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="How we handle your data and protect your privacy."
>
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl px-6 py-12 lg:py-16">
    <header class="mb-12">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-muted-foreground">
        Last updated: January 2026
      </p>
    </header>

    <div class="prose prose-neutral dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
      <p class="text-lg border-l-2 border-muted pl-4 mb-8">
        <strong>TL;DR:</strong> This website respects your privacy. We don't track you, collect personal data, or use invasive analytics.
      </p>

      <h2>What We Don't Collect</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Personal information</li>
        <li>Email addresses (except through Substack)</li>
        <li>Browsing behavior or tracking data</li>
        <li>Cookies for tracking purposes</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>What We May Collect</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Server logs:</strong> Standard web server logs may temporarily store IP addresses for security</li>
        <li><strong>Theme preference:</strong> Your dark/light mode preference is stored locally in your browser</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
      
      <h3>Newsletter (Substack)</h3>
      <p>
        Newsletter subscriptions are managed through Substack. See <a href="https://substack.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Substack's Privacy Policy</a>.
      </p>

      <h3>RSS Feeds</h3>
      <p>
        RSS feed subscriptions are anonymous. We cannot track or identify RSS subscribers.
      </p>

      <h2>Hosting</h2>
      <p>
        This website is hosted on Cloudflare Pages. No personal data is stored in databases.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Questions? Email <a href="mailto:info@gokhanturhan.com">info@gokhanturhan.com</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
